Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P9311 Finance, Taxation, and Monetary Policy.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>ECON  Economic Indicators.
    ECON  Industrial production.
    ECON  Balance of trade.
    ECON  Inflation.
